OL,3,CGlamorgan sack head coach after
OL,4,Cinappropriate behaviour allegations
OL,6,FGlamorgan Cricket have sacked head
OL,7,Fcoach Grant Bradburn after allegations
OL,8,Fof inappropriate behaviour were made
OL,9,Fagainst him.
OL,11,FThe club referred Bradburn to the
OL,12,Findependent cricket regulator after
OL,13,Freceiving the allegations.
OL,15,FThe 58-year-old New Zealander was
OL,16,Fsubsequently charged with misconduct
OL,17,Fand has been sacked with "immediate
OL,18,Feffect," Glamorgan Cricket said.
