OL,3,CGlamorgan sack head coach after
OL,4,Cinappropriate behaviour allegations
OL,6,F"We are confident that a fair and
OL,7,Ftransparent process has been followed
OL,8,Fin this case," read a Glamorgan
OL,9,Fstatement on Monday (30 December).
OL,11,F"Glamorgan Cricket has a zero-
OL,12,Ftolerance policy towards
OL,13,Fdiscriminatory behaviour of any kind.
OL,15,F"Having completed our own internal
OL,16,Finvestigation, it became clear that Mr
OL,17,FBradburn's position was untenable, and
OL,18,Fthe club is now providing the
OL,19,Fappropriate support to those affected."
