OL,6,FHe was appointed as Scotland's head
OL,7,Fcoach in 2014 and stayed in the role
OL,8,Funtil 2018, during which time he
OL,9,Fcoached Scotland to an historic first
OL,10,Fvictory against England in a 2017 ODI.
OL,12,FBradburn had a brief spell as Pakistan
OL,13,Fhead coach in 2023 before joining
OL,14,FGlamorgan on a three-year deal in
OL,15,FJanuary 2024.
OL,17,FHe led Glamorgan to One-Day Cup
OL,18,Fsuccess in September and a fifth-place
OL,19,Ffinish in the second division of the
OL,20,FVitality County Championship.
